@startuml
state Ready
state WaitingForPIN
state OptionsMenu
state ProcessingWithdrawal
state DispensingCash
state PrintingReceipt
state ReturningCard

[*] --> Ready : Insert Card
Ready --> WaitingForPIN : Insert Card
WaitingForPIN --> OptionsMenu : Enter PIN
OptionsMenu --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Select Withdrawal
ProcessingWithdrawal --> DispensingCash : Process Withdrawal
DispensingCash --> PrintingReceipt : Dispense Cash
PrintingReceipt --> ReturningCard : Print Receipt
ReturningCard --> Ready : Return Card and Reset

@enduml
